{"tid":143342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張德江轉口風： 只希望特首選舉是君子之爭","createTime":"2017-03-04T14:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T15:53:51.000Z","uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6d45173bd0f95312ce9fcd5fcb26056112ce4f0","tid":143342,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:17:31.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】主管港澳事務的人大委員長張德江與港澳政協委員會面，有委員引述張德江指，中央認為特首需要<span style=\"color: red;\">愛國愛港</span>、<span style=\"color: orange;\">獲港人擁護</span>，亦要<span style=\"color: pink;\">有擔當</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">能駕馭複雜局面，並<strong><ins>要團結香港各界</ins></strong></span>。不過，會上沒有提及中央屬意哪位候選人，<strong><ins>只強調希望今次是君子之爭。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n張德江在北京飯店的金色大廳，與香港和澳門的全國政協委員會面。張德江與多名政協委員握手，包括常委李家傑及李澤鉅等。<br />\n<br />\n陪同出席會面的還包括全國政協副主席董建華和何厚鏵、統戰部部長孫春蘭、港澳辦主任王光亞等。剛增補為政協委員的梁振英，亦獲安排坐在主席台。<br />\n<br />\n張德江最後作重要講話。有委員引述張德江在會上提到，希望特首選舉依法有序順利舉行，並提出中央對特首人選的要求。<br />\n<br />\n多名與會的政協委員均表示，會上沒有提及中央支持哪位候選人，只希望特首選舉是君子之爭。<br />\n<br />\n張德江在會上亦提到，基本法列明中央擁有憲制權力，對特首有實質任命權，並不是橡皮圖章。據了解，張德江亦提及選委要有擔當、需高度負責、堅定投票。<br />\n<br />\n張德江冀特首選舉依法有序舉行<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=212876&amp;refer=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D212876%26refer%3Dshare&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=f3d19872\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D212876%26refer%3Dshare&h=5959d92a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=212876&amp;refer=share</a>"},{"pid":"3ce1575019556ff524637f46b7b9de407cdc2140","tid":143342,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:21:44.000Z","msg":"即係上次係偽君子之爭"},{"pid":"970c39b7a4f777893fbf509a49b23b5d03dfa375","tid":143342,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:23:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EfnbUwEbCVs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEfnbUwEbCVs&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=53b0c39d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EfnbUwEbCVs</a>"},{"pid":"46a348ae86c9fd04e68309027eb664303a97b707","tid":143342,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:05:35.000Z","msg":"支那走狗跟車太貼又落錯注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5582852d06ac1a0e4e478ecdb3f0a78abdfe6090","tid":143342,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:08:03.000Z","msg":"咁大個會唔會呢個時候出口術啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開完會講d咩點知"},{"pid":"28acaa54c03bac892698859dd8d24d65bb2b8cc9","tid":143342,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T15:53:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁大個會唔會呢個時候出口術啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開完會講d咩點知</blockquote><br />\n專見港區政協既場合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}